(646570, 'Slay the Spire', 'Mega Crit', 'Mega Crit', 'We fused card games and roguelikes together to make the best single player deckbuilder we could. Craft a unique deck, encounter bizarre creatures, discover relics of immense power, and Slay the Spire!', '2019-01-23', 'https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646570/header.jpg?t=1774015376', 'https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1774015376', '4'),
