(648350, 'Jurassic World Evolution', 'Frontier Developments', 'Frontier Developments', 'Place yourself at the heart of the Jurassic franchise and build your own Jurassic World. Bioengineer dinosaurs that think, feel and react intelligently to the world around them and face threats posed by espionage, breakouts and devastating tropical storms in an uncertain world where life always finds a way.', '2018-06-11', 'https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/648350/header.jpg?t=1750957705', 'https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/648350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1750957705', '3'),
